Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:06.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:13.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate \Nalliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:38.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.09,0:03:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy entered a fighting competition -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:43.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,in which a winner will get the \NFlare-Flare Fruit as the prize -
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and won the first round.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, Usopp and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,learned about the nightmare \Nin Dressrosa a decade ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...from a toy soldier who is looking to\Ntake down Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there's no preventing me\Nhurting the citizens...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somebody, please kill me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to save this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Don Quixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The country fell into the hands \Nof Doflamingo in just one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believed that King Riku went crazy\Nat that time, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we got in touch with the new king Doflamingo\Nand ended up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so ashamed of myself\Nfor distrusting King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! It's really too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let the innocent king that you \Nall admired so much die for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were soldiers who got killed\Nand who surrendered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you sum it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't add up to a \Nwhole army for a country!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, they must've been feeling angry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsince Doflamingo turned them into toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unknown number of those poor people\Nis the key to our plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Showdown Between the Warlords!\NLaw vs. Doflamingo!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro! Kin'emon!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shout, idiot!\NSomebody's gonna find us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shh! Shh! Please!\N--Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't so sure about that man\Nwho talks so weirdly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like\Nhe did what he had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He collapsed on our way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What is wrong with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker wants me to kill Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish it up before the competition's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThen, you'll get promoted to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an executive of the Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Straw Hat. But I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna get on board Doflamingo's ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not holding a grudge\Nagainst you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done picking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and then\Nhe suddenly collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I got lost.\NI didn't know which way to go, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! There you are, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you killed him already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Dellinger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:34.98,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,DELLINGER - A COMBATANT\NTHE DON QUIXOTE FAMILY (THE DIAMANTE ARMY)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought you were gonna mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:34.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The assassination of Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what can you do?\NHe's a strong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter\Nif you can get it done or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean he wasn't that serious\Nabout the assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want you to follow him about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he told me to finish you off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have told you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...chitchatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:31.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,ON THE IRON BRIDGE CLOSE TO DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you wanted to kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.52,0:09:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, that fool!\NHe looks exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the Op-Op Fruit, huh?\NHow annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I'm correct,\Nyour power has a limit, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've dealt with the meteorite that Fujitora
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brought down and fought me once \Nand then rescued Black Foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much longer it'll last.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet String!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do now, Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dressrosa is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.19,0:11:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Doffy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diamante.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, sorry.\NAre you in the middle of something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot was here\Nso I thought something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were gonna find out what the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:51.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats were up to\Nwith her Glare-Glare Fruit power{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, don't worry about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Diamante.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy Lao G. and others\Nat the entrance to the SMILE factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.02,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoa-whoa, no way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to fight in the finals\Nand make the people happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure you can handle it\Nby yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You make it sound like \NI'm some kind of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only you can do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you make it sound like I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Admit it. You are a genius.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do it if you insist!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo... You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWhile you're drawing my attention as a decoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other members of the Straw Hats\Nare planning to destroy the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you die here,\Nas long as the factory is destroyed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido will kill me once \NI lose all the SMILEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it how your little scenario goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't buy time as you'd hoped\Nand the Straw Hats aren't doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were just using them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you didn't trust them,\Nyou couldn't plan something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you trust...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know\Nthe "D" will blow up a storm again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want, Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! Why didn't you tell me\Nthere was this kinda competition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were having fun while I \Nwas running around the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's not what we're here for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you let that old man beat you?!\NWhat were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Didn't you see my Gum-Gum Thor Elephant Gun?!\N--That's... No mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Bastille!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the "Pirate Hunter" as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NAnd the guy in the Colosseum is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...probably Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:46.32,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"SHARK SLICER" BASTILLE - A NAVY VICE ADMIRAL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:46.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was the winner of Block C, huh? Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he was so strong-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Smoker said, they are in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we catch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, leave them at large for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a bunch of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,infamous pirates, highly-skilled \Nbounty hunters and mercenaries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from the New World\Ngathered in the Colosseum now-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try to catch the Straw Hats\Nand make a scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll know that we're here-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna catch every one of these badasses
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nas they come out of the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna catch them\Nin one fell swoop-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones that already got eliminated are\NDon Chin Jao from Block C and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sai? Boo? Abdullah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I write down these names\Nthat I don't even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know any of these pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about-{\i1}dara{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've messed around the New World!\NThey're very troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were those names again-{\i1}dara{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. Sai, Boo, and Abdullah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:16:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--Sai? Boo?\N--Abdullah?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who are they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard those names-{\i1}dara{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? Who were we here to catch?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how you use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}dono{\i0} told me to call\Nonce we see Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Colosseum has been besieged\Nby the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care?!\NThat was what we came here for!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:36.16,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,OFF THE COAST OF DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! The Snail is ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?! I'm gonna get it then!\N--Oh no, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji? It's me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Chopper. Call \NUsopp with the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Clank.\N--{\i1}This is Usopp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now we have everybody \Nexcept Law on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sanji on the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}, Chopper, Brook,\NMomonosuke, and Caesar here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.16,0:17:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Kin'emon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in front of the Colosseum\Nwith Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0} and Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. What about you, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Uso...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--This is Franky! I'm with Usopp and Robin!\N--What are you doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.\NWe are currently with...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the King Riku Army, an anti-Doflamingo \Ncoalition in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}An army?{\i0}\N--Of Little People.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little People?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usoland, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a meeting for heroes only.\NDon't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.08,0:17:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We met the strange toy soldier\Noutside of the Colosseum.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Who are the Little People?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was actually\Nthe commander of this army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! The commander of the Little People?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the people here are looking to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take down Doflamingo this very day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is willing to sacrifice his life\Nto destroy this kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's it! The "Toy Soldier"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca wants to stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky, stop the army!\N--{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was thinking the exact opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHave you talked to that girl Rebecca?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh-huh! She is a really nice girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She didn't have much money\Nbut she bought me three lunch boxes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despite that, once she entered in the ring,\Nthe audience jeered at her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't agree more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy, I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't follow Tra-guy's plan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What're you saying, Franky?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I remember his plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After destroying the SMILE factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll keep Doflamingo alive and \Nuse him to take down Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's gonna happen to these people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who're looking to bring \Ndown Doflamingo today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stop these Little People.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like everybody's happy at first\Nbut this country has a very dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...getting ready to fight a deadly battle\Nto get rid of that dark side!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty small\Nbut they have big balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brave, little army is going to challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their filthy, monstrous enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.93,0:19:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...let them down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think it's better for us\Nif Doflamingo wins the battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}'s gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.96,0:20:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Franky!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening there?!
